{"tid":1285030,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Diu你老味真係變第一身視角?!] 《暗黑4》即將公佈？暴雪已持有“diablo4.com”域名","createTime":"2019-07-04T11:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T21:40:28.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff321df1af9e6eaf22e42f668f9776ba0ad14471","tid":1285030,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2372636896340151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2372636896340151&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=41ff016e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2372636896340151</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CedkTN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCedkTN9.png&h=62abf75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【業界】《暗黑4》即將公佈？暴雪已持有&ldquo;<a href=\"http://diablo4.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiablo4.com&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6cd619e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">diablo4.com</a>&rdquo;域名</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  最近，國外玩家RandomMan00做了一些研究，他發現暴雪自2019年1月起恢復了&ldquo;<a href=\"http://diablo4.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiablo4.com&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6cd619e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">diablo4.com</a>&rdquo;域名的持有，而此域名在2002年創建以來，一直處於待售狀態。從域名查詢網站dnsquery 上我們可以看到，目前&ldquo;<a href=\"http://diablo4.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiablo4.com&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6cd619e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">diablo4.com</a>&rdquo;這個域名的註冊/管理/技術公司都是暴雪娛樂，因此我們可以預見到的是暴雪已經開始為這方面做準備了。<br />\n<br />\n  另外值得一提的是，&ldquo;<a href=\"http://diablo3.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiablo3.com&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=cfac0e62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">diablo3.com</a>&rdquo;這個域名是在2008年暗黑3正式公佈前一個月才發現的。因此，如果和《暗黑3》的宣傳節奏類似，那麼本屆嘉年華上我們也許可以看到《暗黑4》的些許消息。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPKPM79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPKPM79.png&h=2a2d18ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀︰<br />\n<strong><ins>[暴雪末日] 暴雪離職員工爆料：整個公司的情緒十分糟糕 3個月內有4個項目被砍掉</ins></strong><br />\n關於《暗黑破壞神4》：是用Overwatch引擎製作的第一人稱遊戲，初始有3個職業，後續計劃增加5個作為季票獎勵，計劃在2021上線，這次是和惡魔站在一起反抗天使<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1264845/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1264845/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ee77eea049d200f7ccf7e32f71b8700f4214cbb6","tid":1285030,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa4ecf9cedd7dde9c61fc7dd1d5719bd8ca4d0f","tid":1285030,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5835a72b6aac0f51652258157029fe72bb017ce","tid":1285030,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T21:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}